ESSAY: In this story, a middle-aged bag of shit develops a one-sided crush on a schoolgirl he barely knows. Due to mental illness, the shitbag feels deeply betrayed when, one day, he happens to see her kissing a boy. Fortunately, he is promptly splattered across the pavement, dead. Unfortunately, his spirit returns to possess the poor girl's body. Having received this incredible gift, he decides to ruin her life and kill her. [REVENGE!] Though he devotes himself to the sexual degradation of the girl's body, he fails to end her life. Her heartbroken boyfriend, however, commits suicide. The boyfriend's spirit then gets a chance to possess the girl's body, presumably intent on ruining her life some more. [REVENGE2!] ..... All this because some loser saw a pretty girl being happy for a moment. So fucking depressing, and not in the least bit hot. That said, it is rather subversive.
